<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>عَبْدُ الرَّزَّاقِ،<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>٤٢٧٢ - عَنِ ابْنِ جُرَيْجٍ،<span class="c5"> عَنْ عَطَاءٍ قَالَ:</span> قُلْتُ: فِيمَا جُعِلَ الْقَصْرُ فِي الْخَوْفِ وَقَدْ أَمِنَ النَّاسُ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«السُّنَّةُ»</span>،<span class="c5"> قُلْتُ:</span> وَرُخْصَةٌ؟<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> <span class="c2">«نَعَمْ»</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>